summary: Airbnb cabin triples in price after appearing in Avengers: Endgame
title: Airbnb cabin triples in price after appearing in Avengers: Endgame
body:
Many people have grown up running around living rooms, jumping over couches and fighting invisible enemies with dressing gowns flapping behind as they lived out their dreams of being a superhero.

And while not many pint-sized warriors graduated into real-life superheroes, there’s still a chance for keen fans to live like one.

The cabin Tony Stark lived in with Pepper Potts and [spoiler] daughter Morgan in Avengers: Endgame is available for rent on Airbnb, but since appearing in the hit film, staying there might cost you a lot more than it would have previously.

However, it appears the volume of interest (at last count 500 views in hours) has seen the listing go offline.

But not before the price of the cabin hit $1,152.11 per night. According to Cinemablend and Comic Book, that price was two thirds lower just days ago.

Hosted by Ed, the lakeside cabin is located in Atlanta, Georgia and can host six guests.

It has three bedrooms, four bathrooms, a cozy fireplace and wraparound balcony.

“Set on private property in the middle of beautiful Bouckaert Farm and home of Chattahoochee Hills Eventing this guest cabin can be your home away from home,” Ed described.

“Need to get away from it all without traveling more than 30 minutes from Atlanta? Need to have a corporate retreat with your elite team? Need to come take the kids fishing and watch a horse show? Then this is your place.

  • Related story: Revealed: The superheroes making Marvel the most money

  • Related story: The number behind ‘Avengers: Endgame’ box office records

  • Related story: Posh suburb says 'Yabba Dabba Don’t’ to ‘eyesore’ Flintstones House

“Avengers Endgame fans… Would you like to stay in Tony Stark’s cabin? This is the iconic cabin in the movie!”

Former guests described the home as a “beautiful and peaceful place” and enthused about the wraparound balcony.

The home has scored five stars based on its three reviews.

It’s not just Avengers: fans can also rent Reese Witherspoon’s house from Big Little Lies

With its floor to ceiling windows and moody beachfront views, the home owned by Reese Witherspoon’s character, Madeline Mackenzie is as memorable as her larger than life character.

And keen fans can even rent the property. Available on Malibu Luxury Vacation Homes (not Monterrey, where the show is set), the home hosts 12 people and costs AU$7,230 a night.

The home also featured in Disney’s Hannah Montana, starring Miley Cyrus.

Check it out:

blog.title: For the record - I'm proud of you.
blog.description:
BEFORE "FOLLOWING" THIS BLOG & SENDING ASKS, PLEASE FIND A WAY TO READ THROUGH ALL THE INFO, SCROLLING TIL THE END! 
Update: This blog is on permanent TV spoiler talk hiatus! This means I will not reply to most asks, messages, comments. I will post "my thoughts" on spoilery scoop in posts I make, and I have nothing to add, so no need to ask, my thoughts are already posted.    
Blog rule #1: Spoilers are not facts or knowledge. Having access to spoilers does not make anyone better or special. 
Blog rule #2: Facts matter, Feelings don't. 
About: Name: Ann. Female. Aspie. Nerdy. TV fan. Introvert. Atheist. NOT american. Low EQ, high IQ. Very opinionated & "sarcastic". Facts before Feelings. Allergic to people who do not google things & who don't read "FAQ" before asking &  don't have interest in finding answers on their own. 
Blog description:  IS HERE  
I'm not associated with any tv show or network. This is simply a blog run by the most boring tv fangirl...ever. 
I TALK ...A LOT...AND DON'T SAY ANYTHING. If you have a problem with long, babbling text posts, stay far away... I only do long posts & long replies!  
This blog is not designed to be viewed on mobile device (reason: image heavy, long posts) 
This blog is NOT spoiler free. Only official scoop, no "gossip" talk! Spoiler rules/info  @FAQ   &  @SCORPION FANS  & under ASK BOX  Most Qs you have are already answered there! 
Asks about peoples personal lives, unreleased spoilers, spoiler sources, plus Qs answered in my recent posts/info pages or in the tags, or things easy to google DO NOT get replied! Check past posts & tags & google things before sending in a new ask!
I share this POV on anons & their take on blogs (like mine) & bloggers (like me) that post/share TV spoilers & thoughts:  READ THIS  
Made you look! #TeamQuintis

body:
Avengers: Endgame: la reazione degli sceneggiatori di Iron Man alla morte di Tony Stark

Gli sceneggiatori Iron Man reagiscono alla morte di Tony Stark in Avengers: Endgame. Art Marcum e Matt Holloway hanno scritto la sceneggiatura per l’Iron Man di Jon Favreau più di 10 anni fa, il film che ha lanciato il Marvel Cinematic Universe e ha catapultato Robert Downey Jr. nell’immaginario collettivo dei grandi attori.

Con l’amato attore che saluta l’universo e Stark che se ne va con lui,…

body:
Chris Hemsworth Shares Amazing Video of Thor Singing ‘Hurt’

With the ban on behind-the-scenes videos lifted from the actor’s phones, most of the Avengers cast is finally going through their pictures and videos from the filming of Avengers: Endgame. We’ve been seeing pics and videos from the filming of the portals scene, as well as the funeral (which they filmed as a wedding), and now Chris Hemsworth has shared what is perhaps the best.

Thor himself shared…
